<span class="postbody">Somebody on the official board told me that what you're looking for looks like a scroll on top of a box.  Also, if you don't find it before the mobs get back, you don't have to start over.  You can just kill them personally <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />.
<br />

<br />
I haven't got around to checking again because I dislike running into Stonetalon and I'm saving it for the weekend (and playing my baby warrior in the mean time).  I really don't think you should have to fight green-or-lower mobs to get to places you've already been, but I've seen no mention of plans to change agro radius for green/gray mobs any further so I guess we're out of luck there.
<br />

<br />
In CoH, too-low-for-xp mobs wont attack you even if you stand on top of them and taunt them!  They might even run away!  The "serious" MMOGs could really learn something from their little brother.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
