<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">If it's the same drop Horde players get - "plans" drop from Operators in stonetalon.  There are 2 good spots to find Operators - one is a building near the creek - second is a logging machine to the south near the road/path that leads south to the deepmoss spider / egg area and eventually sunrock retreat / charred vale to the west.
<br />

<br />
- edit - 
<br />

<br />
The drop is kind of rare - about 1 in 10 operators have it.  It is however, multi-drop - meaning everyone in your group can loot from the same mob.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
